    <text type="note" xml:lang="ru" xml:id="letter-09132"> 
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <date when-custom="1791-07-21">1791 г. 21 июля.</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            <p>Прошу к <date when-custom="1791-07-22">завтрему</date> достать <title ref="works.xml#istros03">третий том <persName ref="people.xml#stc02">Щербатова</persName> гистории</title>
                <note type="editorial">
                    This note might reflect Catherine's interest for Russian history, which A.V. Khrapovitskii writes about in his diary under <date when-custom="1791-06-22">June 22</date>: "Принялись за Российскую Историю", and <date when-custom="1791-06-23 1791-06-24">June 23 and 24 1791</date>: "Упражняются в продолжении Истории Российской" (
                 <bibl>
                    <title ref="works.xml#dnevni01">Dnevnik A.V. Khrapovitskogo 1782-1793</title>
                    , <biblScope unit="pp">pp. 265.</biblScope>
                </bibl>
                ).
                </note>
            </p>
        </body>
